---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Musical Journey - Rohan">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-50 via-white to-primary-50 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Musical Journey</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        "Music is the universal language that connects hearts across cultures. Through piano and sitar, 
        I explore the beautiful intersection of Western and Eastern musical traditions."
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Musical Timeline -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-16">My Musical Timeline</h2>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Timeline line -->
        <div class="absolute left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-primary-200 lg:left-1/2 lg:transform lg:-translate-x-px"></div>
        
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- Timeline Item 1 -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center lg:justify-center">
            <div class="absolute left-6 w-4 h-4 bg-primary-600 rounded-full lg:left-1/2 lg:transform lg:-translate-x-2"></div>
            <div class="ml-16 lg:ml-0 lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8">
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-medium mb-2">Age 6 - 2010</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">First Piano Lesson</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  My musical journey began when my grandmother gifted me a small keyboard. 
                  The magic of creating melodies instantly captivated me, setting the foundation for a lifelong passion.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Timeline Item 2 -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center lg:justify-center">
            <div class="absolute left-6 w-4 h-4 bg-accent-600 rounded-full lg:left-1/2 lg:transform lg:-translate-x-2"></div>
            <div class="ml-16 lg:ml-0 lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8 lg:text-right">
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="text-sm text-accent-600 font-medium mb-2">Age 12 - 2016</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">First Public Performance</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  Performed Chopin's "Minute Waltz" at my school's talent show. 
                  The encouraging applause from my peers gave me confidence to pursue music more seriously.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Timeline Item 3 -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center lg:justify-center">
            <div class="absolute left-6 w-4 h-4 bg-warm-600 rounded-full lg:left-1/2 lg:transform lg:-translate-x-2"></div>
            <div class="ml-16 lg:ml-0 lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8">
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="text-sm text-warm-600 font-medium mb-2">Age 15 - 2019</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Discovering the Sitar</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  My grandfather introduced me to the sitar, connecting me with my Indian heritage. 
                  Learning this ancient instrument opened a new world of ragas and Eastern musical philosophy.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Timeline Item 4 -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center lg:justify-center">
            <div class="absolute left-6 w-4 h-4 bg-primary-600 rounded-full lg:left-1/2 lg:transform lg:-translate-x-2"></div>
            <div class="ml-16 lg:ml-0 lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8 lg:text-right">
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-medium mb-2">Age 17 - 2021</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Cultural Fusion Concert</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  Organized my first fusion performance, blending Western classical piano with traditional Indian ragas. 
                  This concert raised funds for music education in underserved communities.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Timeline Item 5 -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center lg:justify-center">
            <div class="absolute left-6 w-4 h-4 bg-accent-600 rounded-full lg:left-1/2 lg:transform lg:-translate-x-2"></div>
            <div class="ml-16 lg:ml-0 lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8">
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="text-sm text-accent-600 font-medium mb-2">Present Day - 2024</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Teaching & Sharing</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  Now teaching music to kids in my community and creating YouTube content that bridges 
                  Eastern and Western musical traditions, inspiring others to explore diverse cultures through music.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Video Gallery -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Performance Videos</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Experience the beauty of cultural fusion through these recordings of my piano and sitar performances.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Video Placeholder 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200 flex items-center justify-center relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="text-center text-primary-800 z-10">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
              </svg>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Chopin Meets Raga Yaman</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">East Meets West</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              A fusion piece where Chopin's Nocturne in E-flat major flows seamlessly into Raga Yaman, 
              showcasing the universal language of emotion in music.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
              <span>12:34</span>
              <span class="mx-2">•</span>
              <span>Dec 2024</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Video Placeholder 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-100 to-accent-200 flex items-center justify-center relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="text-center text-accent-800 z-10">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
              </svg>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Sitar Improvisation</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Morning Raga</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              An improvised performance of Raga Bhairav, traditionally played at dawn, 
              capturing the peaceful transition from night to day through ancient melodies.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
              <span>8:45</span>
              <span class="mx-2">•</span>
              <span>Nov 2024</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Video Placeholder 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-100 to-warm-200 flex items-center justify-center relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="text-center text-warm-800 z-10">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
              </svg>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Community Concert</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Fundraising Performance</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Highlights from my charity concert supporting music education programs for underserved communities, 
              featuring both piano and sitar performances.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
              <span>15:22</span>
              <span class="mx-2">•</span>
              <span>Oct 2024</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Video Placeholder 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-pink-200 flex items-center justify-center relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="text-center text-purple-800 z-10">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
              </svg>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Teaching Session</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Music Lesson Highlights</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Behind-the-scenes footage from my music teaching sessions with local kids, 
              showing how music becomes a bridge for cultural understanding and expression.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
              <span>6:18</span>
              <span class="mx-2">•</span>
              <span>Sep 2024</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Why Music Matters to Me</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-xl mb-8">
          Music has taught me that diversity creates beauty. Just as Western classical harmony complements 
          Eastern melodic traditions, our differences in the tech world can create something more beautiful 
          than what we could achieve alone.
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-left">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Cultural Bridge</h3>
            <p>
              Through music, I've learned to navigate between two rich cultural traditions, 
              finding harmony in their differences and strength in their union.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Patient Learning</h3>
            <p>
              Both piano and sitar have taught me patience, discipline, and the importance of 
              celebrating small progress—lessons I apply to my work with neurodiverse students.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>